messages.subject: Using the law of attraction to create the family you desire
messages.msgSnippet: I believe when I am living my best life, being my best self, then what others do will have no impact on my peace. But,if I can model this for my children,
messages.messageBody:
"I believe when I am living my best life, being my best self, then
what others do will have no impact on my peace. But,if I can model
this for my children, what a gift I will give to them: an example of a
person who followed her bliss, lived the life of her dreams and died
with a smile on her face having no regrets."

I think you just summed it up right there!! Beautiful. I enjoyed the
entire post...I really think you should submit it to the Blog
Carnival. Thanks for sharing that Tyra.

Ren
learninginfreedom.com
